modName: Bosmer Veteran Armor Set of Setvi - Eng and Fr - Skyrim
summary:
Add a new (renamed) armor & weapon set into Skyrim.
You can find him into a knapsack in the Riverwood inn entrance.
descriptionHtml:
[b][size=5][center][img]http://www.clipartbest.com/cliparts/LiK/knB/LiKknBjXT.png[/img]

[color=#fff2cc]Add a new (renamed) armor & weapon set into Skyrim.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]You can find him into a knapsack in the Riverwood inn entrance.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Armor & weapon stats:
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Same as the vanilla stuff.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Armor & weapon type:
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Light & 2H.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]
[/color][color=#fff2cc]DLC & required stuff:
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Nothing only vanilla Skyrim.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Done for me, but I want to share it with you.
[/color][color=#fff2cc](Intended like a TESO tribute).
[/color][color=#fff2cc]
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Another renamed items mod done by Setvi.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Thx & hope you enjoy it.

[/color][color=#fff2cc]Sorry for my English.
[/color][color=#fff2cc]Setvi.
[/color]
